1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
[EN] Hi, this is my Big Data project: City Mood x Weather Correlation Analysis.
[ZH] 大家好，这是我的大数据项目：城市情绪与天气相关性分析。

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:11,000
[EN] The question I wanted to answer: do people listen to sadder music when it rains?
[ZH] 我想回答的问题：下雨天，人们会不会听更悲伤的音乐？

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:18,000
[EN] I built a Data Lake pipeline with two APIs: Last.fm for music charts, OpenWeatherMap for weather.
[ZH] 我搭建了 Data Lake 管道，两个 API：Last.fm 音乐榜单，OpenWeatherMap 天气。

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:27,000
[EN] Data flows through three layers: raw JSON, formatted Parquet, combined with CDI, then Elasticsearch and Kibana.
[ZH] 数据经三层：原始 JSON、格式化 Parquet、合并 CDI、然后 Elasticsearch 和 Kibana。

5
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:40,000
[EN] One command: python run_pipeline.py. 39 days, 390 records, 10 cities. About 30 seconds.
[ZH] 一条命令：python run_pipeline.py。39 天，390 条记录，10 个城市。约 30 秒。

6
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:52,000
[EN] City Depression Index: CDI = (1 - valence) x (1 + rain + clouds + humidity).
[ZH] City Depression Index：CDI = (1 - valence) x (1 + 雨天 + 云量 + 湿度)。

7
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:05,000
[EN] Valence: 0 = sad, 1 = happy. Rain adds 0.3, clouds 0.2, humidity 0.1. Rain roughly doubles CDI.
[ZH] Valence：0=悲伤，1=快乐。下雨+0.3，云量+0.2，湿度+0.1。雨天 CDI 约翻倍。

8
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:18,000
[EN] Kibana dashboard: world map with CDI heatmap. Red circles = rainy and sad, green = sunny and happy.
[ZH] Kibana 仪表盘：世界地图 CDI 热力图。红圈=下雨悲伤，绿圈=晴天开心。

9
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:30,000
[EN] Bar chart ranks cities. Line chart shows 39-day trend. Heatmap calendar gives the full picture.
[ZH] 柱状图排名城市。折线图显示 39 天趋势。热力图日历展示全局。

10
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:42,000
[EN] Rain vs CDI overlay: rainfall peaks and CDI peaks match almost perfectly every time.
[ZH] 降雨 vs CDI 叠加图：降雨峰值和 CDI 峰值几乎每次都完美重合。

11
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:55,000
[EN] Results: rainy day CDI averages 0.88, sunny day 0.51. That is 1.74 times higher. p < 0.001.
[ZH] 结果：雨天 CDI 平均 0.88，晴天 0.51。高出 1.74 倍。p < 0.001。

12
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:08,000
[EN] Weather explains 48% of CDI variance. Pearson: humidity r=0.57, clouds r=0.56, rain r=0.49.
[ZH] 天气解释 48% 的 CDI 变异。皮尔逊：湿度 r=0.57，云量 r=0.56，降雨 r=0.49。

13
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:20,000
[EN] Five bonus features: Spark, S3 storage, Airflow DAG, blog post, and the self-invented CDI.
[ZH] 五项加分：Spark、S3 存储、Airflow DAG、博客文章、自创 CDI 指标。

14
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:35,000
[EN] This project took two APIs, built a proper Data Lake, invented a new metric, and proved a real correlation.
[ZH] 这个项目用了两个 API，搭建了规范的 Data Lake，自创了一个指标，验证了真实相关性。

15
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:44,000
[EN] Thank you. Happy to answer questions about architecture, code, or methodology.
[ZH] 谢谢。很乐意回答关于架构、代码或方法的任何问题。
